272
00:25:58,003 --> 00:25:58,879
Apa?

273
00:26:01,924 --> 00:26:03,801
Waktu kita tak banyak,

274
00:26:06,136 --> 00:26:07,638
dan tidak ada

275
00:26:08,972 --> 00:26:10,182
yang bisa kita lakukan.

276
00:26:15,145 --> 00:26:16,563
Bu.

277
00:26:54,630 --> 00:26:55,673
Nam-hyeon.

278
00:27:11,022 --> 00:27:15,276
Sebaiknya kau katakan semuanya
dengan jujur

279
00:27:15,943 --> 00:27:18,029
selagi aku masih bisa tenang.

280
00:27:18,946 --> 00:27:22,033
Dalam beberapa hari,

281
00:27:22,116 --> 00:27:23,451
kau menghilang,

282
00:27:23,743 --> 00:27:27,872
lalu Ketua Yu, Jun-hyeong, Petugas Choe,
serta Seung-hui...

283
00:27:28,456 --> 00:27:30,208
Mereka dibunuh, Berengsek.

284
