287
00:27:42,011 --> 00:27:43,346
Apa semua ini kebetulan?

288
00:27:44,555 --> 00:27:45,556
Bagaimana?

289
00:27:49,936 --> 00:27:52,021
Jawab aku, Berengsek. Bagaimana?

290
00:27:52,105 --> 00:27:54,899
Katakan sesuatu, Bedebah!

291
00:27:55,691 --> 00:27:56,859
Nam-hyeon.

292
00:27:59,946 --> 00:28:02,156
Aku bisa bilang apa?

293
00:28:04,450 --> 00:28:06,244
Dari mana memulainya?

294
00:28:06,327 --> 00:28:07,453
Bajingan.

295
00:28:07,537 --> 00:28:10,790
Jika kau bilang Hwang Dae-du pelakunya,
aku akan membunuhmu.

296
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:14,460
Bajingan itu meneleponmu
dari ponsel Ketua Yu!

297
00:28:15,169 --> 00:28:16,003
Siapa dia?

298
00:28:18,005 --> 00:28:18,965
Hwang Dae-du.

299
00:28:19,048 --> 00:28:23,136
Astaga, dasar gila. Kumohon sadarlah!

300
00:28:23,261 --> 00:28:25,304
Berengsek!

301
