dia menyelamatkan nyawa Jun-hyeong.

304
00:28:35,356 --> 00:28:38,151
Namun, dia menembak Jun-hyeong, Bedebah.

305
00:28:38,234 --> 00:28:42,155
Setelah itu, dia menembak diri sendiri.

306
00:28:42,238 --> 00:28:44,323
Dia menembak kepalanya sendiri.

307
00:28:45,825 --> 00:28:49,287
Sementara itu terjadi,
Petugas Choe dan Seung-hui

308
00:28:50,121 --> 00:28:54,125
ditembak dan tewas.

309
00:28:55,001 --> 00:28:57,795
Sejauh apa keterlibatanmu
dalam kejadian ini?

310
00:28:57,879 --> 00:28:59,922
Apa saja yang kau tahu?

311
00:29:00,006 --> 00:29:02,550
Kumohon katakan sesuatu!

312
00:29:04,343 --> 00:29:05,428
Nam-hyeon.

313
00:29:21,068 --> 00:29:22,528
Bodoh.

314
00:29:59,857 --> 00:30:00,691
Ibu.

315
00:30:01,567 --> 00:30:02,693
Seo-jeong.

316
00:30:07,323 --> 00:30:08,366
Kenapa melakukannya?

317
00:30:10,868 --> 00:30:13,204
Kenapa melakukan hal sebodoh itu?

318
00:30:17,834 --> 00:30:18,918
Ibu.

319
00:30:20,837 --> 00:30:22,755
Anakku yang malang.

320
00:30:27,051 --> 00:30:28,094
Seo-jeong.

321
00:30:29,345 --> 00:30:30,304
Kau...

322
00:30:31,639 --> 00:30:33,349
Kau tak boleh mati seperti ini.

323
00:30:36,352 --> 00:30:37,353
Kau harus...

324
00:30:41,691 --> 00:30:44,819
mati di tangan Kang Pil-seong.

325
00:30:49,448 --> 00:30:51,117
Jika tidak,

326
00:30:52,118 --> 00:30:54,829
kau akan melanggar aturan mainnya.

327
00:31:13,306 --> 00:31:15,600
Nona, kau cukup kuat untuk melawanku.

328
00:31:17,018 --> 00:31:18,936
Kenapa kau menjadi lemah?

329
00:31:20,313 --> 00:31:21,731
Hwang Dae-du.

330
00:31:22,398 --> 00:31:25,151
Ada batas tipis
antara derita dan kenikmatan.

331
00:31:25,651 --> 00:31:27,069
Saat ini,

332
00:31:27,653 --> 00:31:29,071
